turned into a
caramel. So I removed the pears,
reduced the

49:51.222 --> 49:54.225 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
liquid to a caramel, and
finished it with
cream.

49:54.258 --> 50:00.631 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The third time, I used Bosc
